{
  "text": "The graphite flakes, poly(vinylidene fluoride-co-hexafluoropropylene) (PVDF-c-HFP) (MW 455 kDa), N,N dimethylformamide (DMF), potassium permanganate (KMnO [CITATION_1] Synthesis of Pt/rGO and Pt/rGO/CB hybrid electrocatalysts",
